thread.title: CG in Williamsburg VA
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by CG in Williamsburg VA

author: CG in Williamsburg VA
title: CG in Williamsburg VA
text:
I am glad I found Vital Choice. The Alaska King Salmon is excellent. The wild organic blueberries are also excellent. I now have a steady supply of both whereas before it was hit or miss wether the grocery store had those items in stock.
The service is also excellent. Food comes very well frozen and promptly.
